{"tid":1713480,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[經典重溫]冠忠再申金鐘禁制令","createTime":"2019-11-12T17:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T02:59:39.000Z","uid":260292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3f877b8ed083553f5d182f6efb2bed3a19bf20c9","tid":1713480,"uid":260292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:42:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20141102/18920969\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20141102%2F18920969&d=QaIhKqS2ROfvs0VeIWBCOlcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=6a44f48f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20141102%2F18920969&h=013b052a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20141102/18920969</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2014-11-02</span></span><br />\n<br />\n【雨傘革命　第36天】<br />\n【本報訊】佔領行動踏入第36天，繼早前有人就佔領地區申請禁制令，並獲頒臨時禁制令，冠忠巴士集團前日再出招，入稟高院就金鐘佔領區申請禁制令，涉及範圍更廣。其三間附屬公司要求開通香港大會堂對開干諾道中東行線、往金鐘的夏愨道東行線及往半山的一段紅棉路，並要求法庭頒令禁制佔領者干預原告或警方拆走路障。"},{"pid":"f5935072c95643c7ac1735bc30fbc49878b8ae4f","tid":1713480,"uid":78857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:46:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20e67d13e762c97e6f587a8b7823e1a1a4d0350d","tid":1713480,"uid":165598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:47:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"468d811216ff9369684a09837208b25b190fb58a","tid":1713480,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:49:13.000Z","msg":"拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"441e215e7285a2ff36f67ea81cbf3338c0a4e1c9","tid":1713480,"uid":